le in the provided content.\n</result>', include_extracted_content_only_once=True, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Opened new tab with URL https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/cakes-cookies-contest-winners/', extracted_content='рҹ”—  Opened new tab with url https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/cakes-cookies-contest-winners/', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Extracted content from https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/cakes-cookies-contest-winners/ for query: List all prize details mentioned on this page, including prize names and any associated descriptions.\nContent saved to file system: Extracted content saved to file extracted_content_4.md successfully. and displayed in <read_state>.', extracted_content='<url>\nhttps://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/cakes-cookies-contest-winners/\n</url>\n<query>\nList all prize details mentioned on this page, including prize names and any associated descriptions.\n</query>\n<result>\nGrand Prize:\u202fScotcharookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңI wanted a bakeryвҖ‘style cookie with the rich flavor and experience of a scotcharoo. I searched for recipes but came up empty, so I made my own, starring the classic combo of peanut butter, chocolate and Rice Krispies.вҖқ вҖ” Ellen Mathewson, Bartonville, Illinois  \n\n1st Place:\u202fCranberry Orange Layer Cake with Rosemary  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңThis special layer cake has a refreshing orange flavor with a hint of rosemary. Since itвҖҷs an oilвҖ‘based cake, it is easy to make and also has a tender crumb. Garnish with sugared cranberries and rosemary for an elevated look.вҖқ вҖ” Lindsay Graham, Conestoga, Pennsylvania  \n\n2nd Place:\u202fClassic Almond Ricotta Cake  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңAfter I started making homemade ricotta cheese, I was inspired to use it in desserts, not just savory dishes. This meltвҖ‘inвҖ‘yourвҖ‘mouth cake is full of almond flavor. It is elegant enough to serve as a dessert for guests, while simple enough for a sweet snack during the week. Add ingredients like lemon zest or fresh blueberries for a change of pace.вҖқ вҖ” Carrie Dault, Baxter, Tennessee  \n\n3rd Place:\u202fButterscotch Pecan Pound Cake  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңMy father just loves nuts and anything butterscotch flavored, so IвҖҷm always on the lookout for recipes that combine these two favorites of his (and mine as well). I altered a cream cheese pound cake recipe to come up with this butterscotch pecan version, and I think itвҖҷs even tastier than the original. For more intense brown sugar flavor, use dark instead of light brown sugar. IвҖҷve also substituted walnuts for pecans with great results.вҖқ вҖ” Lisa Varner, El\u202fPaso, Texas  \n\nMost Innovative:\u202fRed Velvet Cheesecake Cookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңCream cheese and red velvet cake go together like bread and butter, so I figured why not make a cheesecakeвҖ‘filled red velvet cookie? The key ingredient here is farmer cheese: a denser, drier cheese similar in texture to feta. It keeps the filling from being too soft and gives the sweet cookie a little bit of tang.вҖқ вҖ” Kristyne Mcdougle Walter, Lorain, Ohio  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fAlmond Joy Cupcakes  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңI created these Almond Joy cupcakes for my daughter, Julianna, after our spring break trip to Fort Lauderdale. I wanted to thank her for the вҖҳjoyвҖҷ she brought me during our time together. SheвҖҷs a huge help to me in the kitchen and a big inspiration in my life.вҖқ вҖ” Jennifer Gilbert, Brighton, Michigan  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fCaramel Apple Toffee Cookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңI had bags of caramel bits and toffee bits in my pantry that I needed to use, and thatвҖҷs how these cookies were born. The combination of chewy caramel and fresh apple is amazing.вҖқ вҖ” Pamela Shank, Parkersburg, West\u202fVirginia  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fCherry Cordial Cookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңThis is handsвҖ‘down my mostвҖ‘requested cookie recipe at holiday gatherings. These cookies are reminiscent of chocolateвҖ‘covered cherries, so they are a decadent treat.вҖқ вҖ” Noelle Myers, Grand\u202fForks, North\u202fDakota  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fChocolateвҖ‘CoveredвҖ‘Strawberry Shortbread  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңI wanted to create a cookie that embraced chocolateвҖ‘covered strawberries, so I started riffing on shortbread. It took a few tries, but I nailed it with this version! FreezeвҖ‘dried strawberries lend big berry flavor without making the cookies soggy. Be sure to use goodвҖ‘quality chocolate, too.вҖқ вҖ” Jennifer Nystrom, Pooler, Georgia  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fCopycat Samoa Cookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңWe love Girl Scout cookies, especially Samoas, but you can only buy those once a year. I started tweaking a triedвҖ‘andвҖ‘true noвҖ‘bake cookie recipe and wound up with this Samoa tasteвҖ‘alike. ItвҖҷs a great recipe to make with kids!вҖқ вҖ” Donna Gribbins, Shelbyville, Kentucky  \n\nRunnerвҖ‘Up:\u202fKey Lime Pie Cookies  \n\u202f\u202fDescription: вҖңI love baking cookies for family and friends. I was getting bored making the same cookies over and over again, so I decided to come up with my own. My love of Key lime pie inspired these.вҖқ вҖ” Suzy Wade, Deltona, Florida\n</result>', include_extracted_content_only_once=True, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory="File 'results.md' not found.", extracted_content="File 'results.md' not found.", include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Data written to file results.md successfully.', extracted_content='Data written to